data.description: Build memories in this charming 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home in Martins Grove. Inviting you in are stunning wood-look floors and an abundance of natural light from large windows. The bright and airy living room transitions seamlessly into the kitchen, outfitted with sleek appliances and ample counter space for easy serving. After a long day, retire to the spacious primary bedroom, complete with an en suite bathroom boasting a dual sink vanity, soaking tub, and a shower. A sliding glass door leads to your backyard oasis, featuring a covered patio, resort-style screened-in pool, and lush landscaping. This home is conveniently located near Lake Harris, shopping, dining, and more!
